    And  the pod named "doublecontainers" becomes ready
    Given the second user is cluster-admin
    And I login via web console
    When I perform the :check_pod_metrics_tab web action with:
      | project_name | <%= project.name %> |
      | pod_name     | <%= pod.name %>     |
